Package: epuR
Type: Package
Title: Retrieve the Economic Uncertainty Index Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lingbing Feng
Maintainer: Lingbing Feng <fenglb88@gmail.com>
Description: Retrieves the Economic Policy Uncertainty and related index data from the official 
 website <https://www.policyuncertainty.com/index.html> in real time. Provides a consistent framework
 to collect the data and deals with the date format problem.
License: GPL
URL: https://github.com/Lingbing/epuR
BugReports: https://github.com/Lingbing/epuR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: openxlsx, xts, zoo, stats, stringr, lubridate, data.table
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, dygraphs
